            "heading": "WHO WE ARE",
            "heading_color": "#222222",
            "heading_size": 48,
            "heading_weight": "700",
            "heading_spacing": 20,
            "paragraph_text": "<p>We are triathlon athletes based in Asia.We train before work. We race on weekends. We understand what it takes to prepare for the start line and what matters when it gets hard.<br/><br/>5DLA was built from that experience.<br/><br/>We saw a gap. Many of the best endurance products in the world were not easily accessible in Asia, or were available without proper support, sizing, or context.<br/>So we decided to build something ourselves.<br/><br/>A platform that brings high-quality performance apparel and equipment from around the world into Asia-Pacific.<br/>A place where athletes can find what they actually need to improve.<br/><br/>Not more noise. Not more trends.<br/>Just better tools for better performance.<br/></p>",
            "desktop_width_percent": 100,
            "padding": 40,
            "background_color": "#f5f5f5",
